      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:30:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sunnova 首席执行官认为拜登的气候激励措施不会消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/sunnova-ceo-doesn-t-see-biden-climate-incentives-going-away</link>
      <description><![CDATA[屋顶太阳能公司 Sunnova Energy International Inc. 的负责人预计，如果唐纳德·特朗普在 11 月当选总统，总统乔·拜登的清洁能源激励措施不会取消。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/sunnova-ceo-doesn-t-see-biden-climate-incentives-going-away</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:10:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯任命辛瓦尔为政治领袖，削弱停火希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/hamas-says-leader-yahya-sinwar-will-also-become-political-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯任命 10 月 7 日袭击事件的幕后主谋叶海亚·辛瓦尔为其新政治领导人，这是对达成加沙停火协议的多边努力的最新打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/hamas-says-leader-yahya-sinwar-will-also-become-political-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺贝尔奖得主尤努斯将领导孟加拉国临时政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/yunus-to-head-bangladesh-s-interim-government-jamuna-tv-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺贝尔经济学奖得主穆罕默德·尤努斯被任命为孟加拉国临时政府首脑，这是该国在数周的抗议活动迫使前总理谢赫·哈西娜离开后走向稳定的转折点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/yunus-to-head-bangladesh-s-interim-government-jamuna-tv-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:08:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国警方警告暴徒，周三将发生更多骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国警方增派了警力，并表示如果极右翼活动分子按照网上流传的计划于周三晚聚集在移民中心，他们准备逮捕数百名极右翼活动分子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/uk-police-warn-rioters-as-more-unrest-planned-for-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
